    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Book8 — provisioning health workflow\n\n**Env (n8n):** `CORE_API_INTERNAL_SECRET`, `N8N_OPS_SECRET` (same as ops-execute-tool webhook), `RESEND_API_KEY`.\n\nEdit **Send Alert Resend** → `to` / `from` (verified domain on Resend).\n\nWebhook URL: `/webhook/provisioning-check` — same header auth as your other ops webhooks if you add it in n8n.",
        "height": 320,
